rtfolios against the hsbc global mining  index sp extended frontier  index msci acwi ex us index and sp em frontier super comp bmi index the firm employs a combination of inhouse and external research while making its investments it was founded in  and is based in london united kingdom with additional offices in coatesville pennsylvania bellevue washington singapore and dubai united arab emirates city of london investment management company limited operates as a subsidiary of city of london investment group plc detailed description  gracechurch streetlondon  ecv asunited kingdomfounded in  phone     fax     wwwcitloncouk key executives for city of london investment management company limited mr barry martin olliff chief executive officer and chief investment officer age  mr thomas wayne griffith chief operating officer mr juan martin garzaron equities chief investment officer age  mr mark d dwyer cfa head of emerging market closedend fund investment management mr christopher ian weaver cfa fund manager age  compensation as of fiscal year  city of london investment management company limited key developments city of london investment management announces resignation of carlos yuste as business development director from the board effective december   aug   the board of city of london investment group announced the resignation of the business development director carlos yuste from the board of city of london investment management to take effect as of december   similar private companies by industry company name region sipp plc europe i plc europe a e taylor financial services limited europe alist equity research limited europe a anthony corporate limited europe recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for 